    
<section>
 <h1>PHOENICS</h1>
 <p>Phoenics which simulates processes involving fluid flow, heat or mass transfer, chemical reaction and combustion in engineering equipment and the environment.<br>
PHOENICS is used in nearly every branch of engineering and science in which fluid flow plays a key role:-
</p>
<ul>
<li>Aerospace</li>
 <li>Automotive</li>
 <li>Chemical</li>
 <li>Combustion</li>
 <li>Electronics Cooling</li>
 <li>Metallurgical</li>
 <li>Power Generation</li>
 <li>Turbomachinery</li>
 </ul>
 </section>



